{"levelId":"sf-04","chapterId":"sf-04","worldId":"sci-fi","title":"星尘维修区：修好飞船","rewards":{"growthPoints":5},"scenes":[{"sceneId":"dock","background":"assets/story/pixel-dialogue-v2/backgrounds/star-dust-dock.png","lines":[{"type":"narration","text":"维修区里，星尘像金色小雨一样落下。飞船的推进器少了一块发光零件。","character":"narrator"},{"type":"dialogue","text":"别担心，我们一起把它修好。","character":"pet","position":"right"},{"type":"activity","activityType":"repair","prompt":"把会发光的零件放回推进器。","character":"star_engineer","position":"center","actions":[{"label":"放入蓝色零件","feedback":"推进器重新转起来了！"},{"label":"拧紧银色螺丝","feedback":"螺丝固定好了，飞船更稳了。"}]},{"type":"dialogue","text":"修好一件小事，也能让大飞船继续前进。","character":"hero","position":"left"}]}]}
